- content_for :body_class, "landing-page"

%section.hero-section.text-white.py-5
  .container
    .row.align-items-center.py-5
      .col-lg-7
        %span.badge.bg-white.text-primary.mb-3.px-3.py-2
          %i.bi.bi-code-slash.me-1
          Open Source
        %h1.display-4.fw-bold.mb-3
          Pay freelancers.
          %br
          Built on POP.
        %p.lead.mb-4{style: "opacity: 0.9;"}
          Bookify is an open-source marketplace that shows you exactly how to
          onboard, manage, and pay freelancers using the
          %strong Payout Partner API.
        .d-flex.flex-wrap.gap-3
          %a.btn.btn-light.btn-lg.px-4{href: users_sign_in_path}
            %i.bi.bi-arrow-right-circle.me-2
            Get Started
          %a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-lg.px-4{href: "https://github.com/payoutpartner/bookify-app", target: "_blank"}
            %i.bi.bi-github.me-2
            View Source

      .col-lg-5.d-none.d-lg-block.text-center
        .hero-illustration
          .card.shadow-lg.border-0.mx-auto{style: "max-width: 380px; transform: rotate(2deg);"}
            .card-body.p-4
              .d-flex.align-items-center.mb-3
                .rounded-circle.bg-primary.text-white.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center{style: "width: 40px; height: 40px;"}
                  %i.bi.bi-person
                %div.ms-3
                  %strong.d-block Anna Freelancer
                  %small.text-muted anna@example.com
              %hr.my-2
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.mb-2
                %span.text-muted Booking
                %span.fw-bold Website Design
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.mb-2
                %span.text-muted Rate
                %span.fw-bold kr 850/hr
              .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
                %span.text-muted Status
                %span.badge.bg-success Paid

%section.py-5
  .container
    .text-center.mb-5
      %h2.fw-bold How it works
      %p.text-muted.lead Three steps from invite to payout
    .row.g-4
      .col-md-4
        .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm.text-center
          .card-body.p-4
            .step-number.mb-3 1
            %h5.fw-bold Invite Freelancers
            %p.text-muted
              Enter their email. They receive an invitation and complete identity verification
              through POP's secure onboarding flow.
      .col-md-4
        .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm.text-center
          .card-body.p-4
            .step-number.mb-3 2
            %h5.fw-bold Create Bookings
            %p.text-muted
              Log work with a description, hours, and rate.
              Bookify handles the tax and compliance through POP.
      .col-md-4
        .card.h-100.border-0.shadow-sm.text-center
          .card-body.p-4
            .step-number.mb-3 3
            %h5.fw-bold Pay Instantly
            %p.text-muted
              Hit pay and POP handles invoicing, tax reporting,
              and bank transfer. The freelancer gets paid to their account.

%section.py-5{style: "background-color: #f0f0ff;"}
  .container
    .text-center.mb-5
      %h2.fw-bold Two sides, one platform
    .row.g-4
      .col-md-6
        .card.border-0.shadow-sm.h-100
          .card-body.p-4
            .d-flex.align-items-center.mb-3
              .rounded-3.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.me-3{style: "width: 48px; height: 48px; background-color: #EEF2FF;"}
                %i.bi.bi-briefcase.text-primary{style: "font-size: 1.4rem;"}
              %h4.fw-bold.mb-0 Booker
            %p.text-muted
              The operator side. Invite freelancers, create bookings,
              trigger payouts, and track everything from your dashboard.
            %ul.list-unstyled
              %li.mb-2
                %i.bi.bi-check2.text-primary.me-2
                Invite freelancers by email
              %li.mb-2
                %i.bi.bi-check2.text-primary.me-2
                Track bookings and payouts
              %li.mb-2
                %i.bi.bi-check2.text-primary.me-2
                One-click payments via POP

      .col-md-6
        .card.border-0.shadow-sm.h-100
          .card-body.p-4
            .d-flex.align-items-center.mb-3
              .rounded-3.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.me-3{style: "width: 48px; height: 48px; background-color: #F0FDFA;"}
                %i.bi.bi-person-badge{style: "font-size: 1.4rem; color: #0D9488;"}
              %h4.fw-bold.mb-0 Freelancer
            %p.text-muted
              The worker side. Accept invitations, verify your identity,
              view bookings, and get paid directly to your bank account.
            %ul.list-unstyled
              %li.mb-2
                %i.bi.bi-check2.me-2{style: "color: #0D9488;"}
                Accept invites with one click
              %li.mb-2
                %i.bi.bi-check2.me-2{style: "color: #0D9488;"}
                Secure identity verification
              %li.mb-2
                %i.bi.bi-check2.me-2{style: "color: #0D9488;"}
                Track your earnings

%section.py-5
  .container
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col-md-8
        .card.border-0.shadow.text-center
          .card-body.p-5
            %i.bi.bi-code-square.display-4.text-primary.mb-3
            %h3.fw-bold Built for developers
            %p.text-muted.mb-4
              Bookify is a fully working Rails app that demonstrates every POP API v2 endpoint.
              Clone it, deploy it, or use it as a reference for your own integration.
            .d-flex.flex-wrap.justify-content-center.gap-2
              %span.badge.bg-light.text-dark.border.px-3.py-2 Rails 8
              %span.badge.bg-light.text-dark.border.px-3.py-2 PostgreSQL
              %span.badge.bg-light.text-dark.border.px-3.py-2 Bootstrap 5
              %span.badge.bg-light.text-dark.border.px-3.py-2 HAML
              %span.badge.bg-light.text-dark.border.px-3.py-2 Heroku-ready
            %hr.my-4
            %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-5{href: "https://github.com/payoutpartner/bookify-app", target: "_blank"}
              %i.bi.bi-github.me-2
              View on GitHub
